a ũmwe, na atĩ gĩtũmi tu gĩa gũtigana nĩ ngomanio itaagĩrĩire. (Mathayo 19: 4-9) Tũkoragwo na ma atĩ ũũgĩ ũrĩa ũkoragwo thĩinĩ wa Bibilia nĩ ũteithagia famĩlĩ igaacĩre. —Aefeso 5:22– 6:1. Ũthathaiya witũ. Tũtihũthagĩra mĩtharaba kana mĩhianano ĩngĩ o yothe ũthathaiya-inĩ. (Gũcokerithia Maathani 4: 15- 19; 1 Johana 5: 21) Ũthathaiya witũ ũkoragwo na maũndũ maya ma bata: Kũhoya Ngai. —Afilipi 4:6. Gũthoma na kwĩruta Bibilia. —Thaburi 1: 1-3. Gwĩcũrania maũndũ marĩa twĩrutĩte Bibilia-inĩ. —Thaburi
